	<h3>1. Create one String-based Handoff</h3>
	<p>
		In <span class="bold_text">STRINGS HANDOFF</span> tab, click the <span class="bold_text">Add new handoff</span> link.
		<img src="<?php echo $this->baseUrl('/images/documents/AddNewHO.jpg');?>" height="18" hspace="0" width="118" border="0">
