	<h3>2. Collect localized Strings and Close one Handoff</h3>
	<p>
		After localization of the String into all target languages, Jonckers PM will Set the HO as "HB - Completed". Client will be notified by email.
	</p>
	<p>
		At this stage, Client will be able to See the Localized Strings in the HO Details. Alternatively Client can export localized strings in an Excel Spreadsheet format.
	</p>
	<p>
	Client confirms reception of Jonckers' HB by Closing the HO.
	</p>
	<p>
		To close the HO, In HANDOFF tab, click Edit
		<img src="<?php echo $this->baseUrl('/images/documents/EditHBCompletedLink.JPG');?>" height="20" hspace="0" width="78" border="0"> for your HO, change its status to <span class="bold_text">HO - Closed</span> and <span class="bold_text">Save</span>.
	</p>
	<p>
		You can choose whether you want to inform Jonckers PM of this status change by keeping the checkbox activated (recommended) or not.
	</p>
	<p>
		<img src="<?php echo $this->baseUrl('/images/documents/SetHOasClosed2.JPG');?>" height="48" hspace="0" width="516" border="0">
	</p>
	<p>
		You will still be able to see/download localized strings in HO Details page, after closure of the HO.
	</p>
